  %% Diagram 47: Buyer Frontend Experience Composition Flow

  Home[Buyer Homepage]
  Search[Search and discovery]
  Reels[Reels and live discovery]
  Product[Product detail page]
  Cart[Cart and coupon stage]
  Checkout[Checkout]
  Tracking[Order tracking]
  Chat[Buyer-vendor chat entry]

  API[REST query/data APIs]
  WS[Realtime order status subscription]
  Error[Recoverable error UI state]
  Retry[Retry fetch with backoff]
  Cached[Show cached snapshot while retrying]

  Home --> Search --> Product --> Cart --> Checkout --> Tracking
  Home --> Reels --> Product
  Tracking --> Chat

  Search --> API
  Product --> API
  Cart --> API
  Checkout --> API
  Tracking --> WS

  API -->|fetch failed| Error --> Cached --> Retry --> API
